Changes

Version 0.3
-----------

New features

 * Deep pattern matching
 * Type signatures
 * Rigid type variables
 * Polymorphic recursion
 * Refinement of polymorphic variant typing to make use of absence
information
 * User defineable operators, precedence and associativity
 * Partial support for Internet Explorer
 * Configuration files
 * Database operations: insert, update and delete

Syntax

 * Tables are now handles rather than lists
 * Tables and databases are first class
 * Changes to DOM API
  * get and set attributes

Miscellaneous bug fixes in

 * mysql driver
 * SQLite driver
 * JavaScript generation
 * type inference
 * database optimisation
